OL,3,CAir fryers causing tens of thousands
OL,4,Cof pounds worth of damage, says insurer
OL,6,FClaims for damage relating to air
OL,7,Ffryers are running into tens of
OL,8,Fthousands of pounds on average, with
OL,9,Fcosts running as high as #80,000, an
OL,10,Finsurance giant is warning.
OL,12,FAviva said it has seen some
OL,13,Fsignificant home insurance claims
OL,14,Frelating to air fryer fires over the
OL,15,Fpast four years, with claimants
OL,16,Fsustaining considerable fire and smoke
OL,17,Fdamage to their homes.
