OL,3,CAir fryers causing tens of thousands
OL,4,Cof pounds worth of damage, says insurer
OL,6,FThe average claim for 2024 amounted to
OL,7,F#29,555 and in one case dealt with by
OL,8,Fthe insurer, an air fryer fire caused
OL,9,F#80,000 worth of damage to a kitchen
OL,10,Fafter spreading and setting the entire
OL,11,Froom alight, destroying the kitchen
OL,12,Fceiling, walls, cupboards and their
OL,13,Fcontents, a washing machine and a
OL,14,Ftelevision.
OL,16,FAviva said that in some cases,
OL,17,Fclaimants have described seeing flames
OL,18,Ferupting from collapsing and melting
OL,19,Fair fryers, destroying the surfaces on
OL,20,Fwhich they were placed.
