OL,6,FIt has also dealt with several claims
OL,7,Fwhere air fryers had been placed on
OL,8,Fhobs, accidentally switching the hob
OL,9,Fon and inadvertently setting the air
OL,10,Ffryer ablaze.
OL,12,FIn one incident, a hungry dog was
OL,13,Fresponsible for a hob being
OL,14,Faccidentally switched on.
OL,16,FThe insurer also commissioned a survey
OL,17,Fby Censuswide, which found that around
OL,18,Ftwo-thirds (68%) of people in the
OL,19,Fresearch own an air fryer.
