OL,6,FHannah Davidson, senior underwriting
OL,7,Fmanager at Aviva, said: "With the
OL,8,Fincreasing popularity of air fryers,
OL,9,Fit's crucial that users are aware of
OL,10,Fthe associated fire risks. Aviva's
OL,11,Fsurvey shows that nearly one in five
OL,12,FUK residents have encountered fire-
OL,13,Frelated issues with air fryers, from
OL,14,Fsmoking and overheating to explosions
OL,15,Fand fires. This, alongside our claims
OL,16,Finsights, underscores the need for
OL,17,Fconstant vigilance."
